761.name: Jildon's Farm Junction
desc: "   You are on a dusty road, surrounded by fields of
grass.  To the north you see some farm buildings
and a small road leading to them.  The road that
you are currently on leads east to the city in the
distance, and west, deeper into the grasslands.
